V0114_01_00_00_0.text:
Since I control fate, you can't win!
Destruction is at hand!

V0114_01_00_01_0.text:
You dare oppose destiny?
Big mistake!

V0114_01_00_02_0.text: The cards predict victory - for me and me alone!

V0114_01_00_03_0.text: You will learn how foolish it is to defy your destiny.

V0114_01_00_04_0.text: You may have changed fate once before, but can you again?

V0114_01_00_05_0.text:
Aster!
Freedom is but an illusion!
You are destined to lose!

V0114_03_00_03_0.text: I know what destiny has in store for you.

V0114_03_00_04_0.text: You seem to have the advantage, but fate tells me otherwise.

V0114_03_00_05_0.text: You will not change my destiny!

V0114_05_00_00_0.text: There's nothing you can do but watch me destroy your future!

V0114_06_01_00_0.text: I know every move you'll make!

V0114_08_00_00_0.text:
I activate my Trap Card!
Arcana Call!

V0114_08_00_01_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Call of the Haunted!

V0114_08_00_02_0.text: I activate the Trap Card, Reversal of Fate!

V0114_08_00_02_1.text: Arcana Force's effect switches to the opposite one!

V0114_08_00_03_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Monster Reincarnation!

V0114_08_00_05_0.text: The Spell Card, Cup of Ace!

V0114_39_00_09_0.text: Since it's right side up, I draw two cards from my Deck!

V0114_39_00_10_0.text:
You should thank me.
You get to draw two cards.

V0114_08_00_12_0.text: Fate will decide Light Barrier's effect!

V0114_39_00_13_0.text:
Fate obeys my every whim!
Right side up!

V0114_39_00_14_0.text:
What? Upside down?
How can this be?

V0114_39_00_15_0.text: As long as I have Light Barrier, destiny cannot change!

V0114_39_00_16_0.text: But Light Barrier shall shine again next turn!

V0114_08_00_17_0.text: The Continuous Trap, Tour of Doom!

V0114_39_00_21_0.text: Life cannot flourish in the land of the doomed!

V0114_09_00_00_0.text: Arcana Force's effect depends on which way the card faces.

V0114_09_00_01_0.text: I know all - so I know this card will be right side up!

V0114_09_00_02_0.text:
Allow me to make a prediction.
It will be right side up!

V0114_09_00_03_0.text:
My control over fate is absolute.
The future will obey me!

V0114_40_00_05_0.text:
There is no changing fate!
The effect is right side up!

V0114_40_00_06_0.text:
As I predicted!
It gains the effect of right side up!

V0114_40_00_07_0.text:
I'm overflowing with the power of destiny!
Right side up!

V0114_40_00_09_0.text: How could my destiny be led astray?

V0114_09_00_12_0.text: Now which one of us will be the fool?

V0114_40_00_14_0.text:
Upside down!
You cannot avoid the whims of fate!

V0114_40_00_15_0.text: The Fool's right side up effect!

V0114_40_00_18_0.text: The Magician's right side up effect!

V0114_09_00_24_0.text: The Empress's right side up effect!

V0114_40_00_27_0.text: The Emperor's right side up effect!

V0114_40_00_33_0.text: The Lovers' right side up effect!

V0114_09_00_36_0.text: The Chariot's right side up effect!

V0114_40_00_39_0.text: The Strength's right side up effect!

V0114_40_00_51_0.text: The Hangman's right side up effect!

V0114_09_00_56_1.text: By discarding Temperance, battle damage becomes 0!

V0114_09_00_70_0.text: The Moon's right side up effect!

V0114_09_00_79_0.text: The World's right side up effect!

V0114_09_00_79_1.text:
Ha!
Fate has decreed that your world ends while mine begins!

V0114_09_00_82_0.text: The Light Ruler's right side up effect!

V0114_09_00_83_0.text: The Light Ruler's upside down effect!

V0114_40_00_85_0.text: The Dark Ruler's right side up effect!

V0114_40_00_86_0.text: The Dark Ruler's upside down effect!

V0114_10_00_02_0.text: Witness what fate has in store for you.

V0114_11_00_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Attack Position!

V0114_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0114_13_00_00_0.text: Join me, Arcana Force 0 - The Fool!

V0114_13_00_01_0.text: I summon Arcana Force I - The Magician!

V0114_13_00_03_0.text: I call Arcana Force III - The Empress!

V0114_13_00_04_0.text: Come forth, Arcana Force IV - The Emperor!

V0114_13_00_06_0.text: Arise, Arcana Force VI - The Lovers!

V0114_13_00_07_0.text: I summon Arcana Force VII - The Chariot!

V0114_13_00_08_0.text: I summon Arcana Force VIII - The Strength!

V0114_13_00_12_0.text: Come to me, Arcana Force XII - The Hangman!

V0114_13_00_18_0.text: Bear witness to Arcana Force XVIII - The Moon!

V0114_13_00_21_0.text:
Hahahaha!
With this card, your existence is over!

V0114_13_00_21_1.text:
The final major arcana!
Arcana Force XXI - The World!

V0114_13_00_22_0.text: I shall call forth the great conqueror to end your destiny!

V0114_13_00_22_1.text: I tribute these three pillars of light!

V0114_13_00_22_2.text: Behold! Arcana Force EX - The Light Ruler!

V0114_13_00_23_0.text: Witness the power that rules over fate!

V0114_13_00_23_1.text: Arcana Force EX - The Dark Ruler!

V0114_16_00_00_0.text: You could've avoided facing this harsh reality.

V0114_16_00_01_0.text: If you only accepted your destiny!

V0114_19_00_21_0.text: Your destiny is to be crushed by me!

V0114_19_00_22_1.text:
The Light Ruler attacks!
Final Ray!

V0114_19_00_23_0.text: You have no strength left to confront your fate!

V0114_21_00_00_0.text: By now, even you know what fate awaits you.

V0114_28_00_00_0.text: You're less than nothing in the grand presence of destiny!

V0114_28_00_00_1.text: You can’t stop what’s meant to be!

V0114_28_00_02_1.text: No matter how hard you strike, you can't leave a mark!

V0114_28_00_03_0.text:
Hahaha...
It is correct that you feel fear.

V0114_28_00_03_1.text: For destiny will punish you for your disobedience!

V0114_28_00_04_1.text: Your HEROES are powerless against the Light of Destruction!

V0114_28_00_05_1.text: I predicted that you'd be begging for my forgiveness!

V0114_29_00_00_0.text: I knew the Light of Destruction was also within you.

V0114_29_00_00_1.text:
For did it not feel great to make me suffer?
Hahahaha!

V0114_29_00_01_0.text:
No no no!
How could this be!

V0114_29_00_04_0.text: The universe is still full of mysteries.

V0114_29_00_04_1.text: One of which Jaden has unlocked to alter destiny.

V0114_30_00_00_0.text:
You want to surrender?
There's no surrender in a fight!

V0114_30_00_01_0.text: You're determined to change fate, but you'll change nothing.

V0114_33_00_00_0.text:
I don't just see.
I foresee!

V0114_33_00_01_0.text: I am bursting with the power of fate!

V0114_34_00_01_0.text: Want me to tell your future?

V0114_34_00_02_0.text: Fate can even make the mighty feel small.

V0114_34_00_03_0.text: Our story has already been written.

V0114_34_00_04_0.text:
Are you sure? 
This is exactly what destiny wants.

V0114_34_00_05_0.text: Fortune says that this Duel will end before my turn.

V0114_34_00_06_0.text: Have you forgotten how to Duel?

V0114_34_00_07_0.text:
Hold on!
Don't be so impatient!

V0114_34_00_08_0.text: Of course it's right side up!

V0114_35_00_00_0.text: Entrust your destiny to my cards.

V0114_36_00_01_0.text: Every event is proceeding as predicted!

V0114_36_00_02_0.text: Destiny has yet to be altered!

V0114_26_00_00_0.text: Is that the best you can do?
